additionalProperty.name: Warning
additionalProperty.value: Intentionally misuse by deliberately concentrating and inhaling contents can be harmful or fatal. Keep out of reach of children. Pressurised dispenser. Extremely flammable. Keep in a cool place out of the sun. Do not store in direct sunlight. Do not expose can to temperatures above 50C. Such as may occur in cars, or near heat sources such as heaters, stoves or incandescent material - no smoking. Do not pierce or burn, even after use. May irritate eyes. Avoid spraying near eyes. For advice, contact a Poison Information Centre (Phone Australia 13 11 26, New Zealand 0800 764 766) or a doctor.
